name: Deep scratch
description:
- What is love?
Some people try to reply to this question with words, others try to explain the love with acts. 
Other people don't even know if they ever felt it. 
Still, other people are afraid to feel it, and to fall in love.
Love is one of the strongest and maybe best things can happen to humans in this world. 
Two souls who merge into one in an alchemical fusion of sensations, feelings and emotions. 
Everything appears different when you are in love.
Everything has different meanings, and the life seems more colorful.
Yes, is really nice.

But what happens if your other soul lets you down?
What happens if love ends?
-

3000 x 7500 px
